Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin mutunci da fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Duk wani kuri'a da aka kada wa Alkalin Kotun Kavanaugh, kuri'a ce da ke nuna rashin amincewa da dabarun da ake amfani da su wajen tayar da zaune tsaye a jam'iyyar Democrat", in ji Trump a wani taron jama'a a birnin Wheeling, a jihar West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin mutunci da fushin jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da yake takara.
Kavanaugh ya shaida wa majalisa a ranar Alhamis, yana musanta zargin da aka yi wa Christine Blaise Ford na cin zarafin jima'i shekaru da yawa da suka gabata lokacin da suke matashi.
