John Edward: Ilimin harshe yana da muhimmanci ga 'yan ƙasa na duniya
Makarantun masu zaman kansu a Scotland suna ci gaba da kasancewa da kyakkyawan matsayi a cikin ilimi, wanda ya ci gaba a cikin 2018 tare da wani kyakkyawan aikin gwaji, wanda kawai ya ƙarfafa ta hanyar mutum da kuma nasarar da aka samu a wasanni, zane-zane, kiɗa da sauran ilimin zamantakewa.
Tare da kusan dalibai 30,000 a duk faɗin Scotland, waɗannan makarantu, waɗanda ƙungiyar Independent Schools of Scotland (SCIS) ke wakilta, suna ƙoƙari su ba da mafi kyawun matakin ga ɗaliban su da iyayensu.
Makarantun masu zaman kansu suna da burin shirya ɗaliban su don ci gaba da iliminsu, zaɓin aikin da suka zaɓa da kuma matsayinsu a cikin duniya.
