Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zaben shugaban kasa a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko na taron Trump guda biyar da aka shirya, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare da aka sani, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Ta hanyar jinkirta zaben tabbatar da zabarsa don cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun kolin, Trump yana nufin tallafawa zaben tsakiyar zangon da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a kan majalisar dokoki a zaben Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana yau da dare kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya ziyarar Trump zuwa Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma, agogon Gabas a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon ziyarar Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai iya duba sauraron wannan makon game da za ~ en na Kotun Koli na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya haifar da tashin hankali game da zargin lalata da jima'i, wanda ya jinkirta amincewa da kuri'ar majalisar dattijai har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu kwarin gwiwa a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya bayyana cewa wadannan gangamin biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, za su taimaka wa masu ba da agaji da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shirinsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kuma muna shiga wani yakin neman zabe mai cike da alkawura", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
Taron na yau da dare, wanda aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, na iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara ta biyu a wannan watan a jihar West Virginia, inda ya samu rinjaye da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya ragu a cikin binciken.
"Ba kyakkyawan alama ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya ba shi damar yin nazarin zamantakewar al'umma", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
