Mene ne bikin 'Global Citizen' kuma shin yana taimakawa wajen rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin 'Global Citizen', wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da manyan masu rawa da kuma aiki mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A yanzu, a shekara ta bakwai, bikin 'yan ƙasa na duniya zai tara dubban mutane a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don ba kawai su ji daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don su san ainihin manufar taron: kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekara ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, ci gaba ne na Global Poverty, wani shiri ne na kasa da kasa wanda ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan ba ku so ku biya tikitin VIP), baƙi sun cika wasu ayyuka ko 'ayyuka' kamar yin aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kira a waya ko kuma tuntuɓar ta wasu hanyoyi don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da aka samu a 'yan ƙasa na duniya shekaru 12 kafin cimma burin?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da kide kide da wake-wake kyauta hanya ce mai kyau ta lallashe su su nemi aiki ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "tambaya" da mutane ke tunanin suna yin wani abu mai ma'ana lokacin da suka sanya hannu kan takarda kai ta yanar gizo ko kuma aika sako a Twitter?
Tun daga 2011, 'yan ƙasa na duniya sun rubuta fiye da miliyan 19 na abubuwan da magoya bayansu suka yi don cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce waɗannan ayyuka sun taimaka wa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane fiye da biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ambata alkawura 390 da sanarwa da suka samo asali daga ayyukanta, daga cikinsu an riga an biya ko an tara aƙalla dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta ce an riga an yi wa kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya allurar rigakafin.
