Mako guda bayan da wata jarida a kasar Sin ta buga wani shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka game da cinikin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi amfani da wata takarda da jaridar China Daily ta wallafa a jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi kowanne a Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa Reuters cewa sabon mataki ne a yakin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
Ko da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su rika tallatawa juna tallace-tallace don su inganta cinikayya, a yanzu haka Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ke kara tsanantawa, inda suke daidaita harajin shigo da kayayyaki tsakanin kasashen.
Masana a Amurka da China sun ce a farkon yakin cinikayya, ana amfani da harajin cinikayya a kasar Sin don yin mummunan tasiri ga masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan jihar Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta ci zarafin ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata sanarwa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, "Yanzu tana ninka wannan zalunci ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"A cikin yada farfagandar da take yi, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin magana da' yan jarida ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a kan kantin jarida a kan titi a nan Beijing, za ku sami iyakancewar magana kuma ba za ku ga ainihin nuna bambancin ra'ayi da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da mummunan yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin tsananin kulawar jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jaridar kasar Sin ta kauce wa tayin buga labarinsa, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wacce ta yi hakan ba.
