Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palau na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, kungiyoyin agaji ba za su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palo, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palau bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Dongola da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palo shine babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ɗan gajeren rairayin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, yana da yawan mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Dongala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tekun tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin wannan yanayin, akwai wasu ƙananan yankuna da ke da ƙananan yankuna.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Harshen nickel ma yana da mahimmanci ga lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne a Morawai, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Masu binciken sun ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunamis ya addabi garin Palo da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗaruruwan gine-gine a Donggala.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a dukan gaɓar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata guguwa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auko wa tsibirin Java mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a gaɓar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta auku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta auku a 2004.
Amma ba a yi tsunami ba, amma an kashe mutane fiye da 100 a lokacin da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu mazauna arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin halin da ba su da mafita.
