Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yankewa Saifullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York City wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar saboda aikata laifi a shekarar 1953.
An yi zargin cewa Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da wata motar haya daga Home Depot don yin harin a watan Oktoba a kan hanyar keke kusa da titin West Side a Lower Manhattan, yana lalata masu tafiya da kekuna a hanyarsa.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saifov ya yi kisan kai ga mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni ga jiki, a cewar sanarwar niyyar da aka gabatar a kan bukatar yanke hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York.
A cewar takardun kotu, duka zargin da ake yi wa 'yan sanda na iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saifov da laifin aikata laifuffuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da suka shafi fashi da fashi, wanda ake amfani da shi a kotun tarayya a lokuta masu rikitarwa, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Wannan hari ya bukaci "tsari mai kyau da kuma niyya", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saifov ya aikata "mummunan, mummunan, da kuma lalata".
Saifullah Habibulayevich Saifov ya haddasa rauni, lalacewa da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Lori Decad, Darren Drake, Ariel Early, Ernan Feluci da Alejandro Damian Panuco, in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
