An tuhumi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar shekarar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa saboda yin ta'addanci da leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg da kuma Robert Rosenberg a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
