Yadda yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai amfanar da Beijing
Farkon harbin da aka yi a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya zama abin ban mamaki, kuma yayin da yakin ke kara karfi, rabuwar tsakanin kasashen biyu zai amfanar da Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadin farko a wannan shekara ta hanyar saka haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminum.
Matsayin da ya fi tsanani ya zo ne a wannan makon da sabbin haraji da ke shafar kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 200 (Fita biliyan 150) tare da sanya haraji a kan rabin kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka kai hari, Beijing ta sake saka wasu haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma cikin dari kan kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta sha alwashin mayar da martani ga duk wani hari da Amurka ta kai mata, kuma ba a sa ran tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu zai yi watsi da hakan ba.
Don sa Washington ta yi watsi da wannan umurni, to ya kamata a yi biyayya da shi, amma yin biyayya ga Washington a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da katunan da suka dace, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya da Amurka zai iya taimakawa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara kan siyasa cikin hanzari a Washington da Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin rikicewar tattalin arziki a cikin ɗayan ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura da su suka yarda", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike kan al'amuran Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Tsaro ta Amurka.
Syria a shirye take ta karbi 'yan gudun hijirar da suka dawo, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da suka dawo gida da son rai kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina ƙasar da ta gamu da rikici na tsawon shekaru bakwai.
A jawabinsa ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Muallem ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
Ya ce, "Yanzu yanayin da ke cikin gida ya fi karko da tsaro, saboda ci gaban da muka samu a yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da aikin gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don mayar da su ga al'adarsu ta yau da kullun.
Yanzu akwai dukkan yanayi da ya kamata don 'yan gudun hijira su koma kasar da suka tsere daga saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye da suka shafi rayuwarsu da kuma yadda suke rayuwa.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a can suna bukatar agajin jin kai.
Al-Muallem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da duk wani taimako da za a bayar don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba za a amince da tallafi ko taimako daga kasashen da ke tallafawa 'yan tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta hanyar doke kungiyar Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a kusa da birnin Paris, Faransa.
A halin yanzu, Amurka ta sha kaye shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar bayan da tawagar Denmark, karkashin jagorancin Thomas Bjorn, ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin lashe gasar.
Tauraron Amurka, Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi rauni a yawancin gasar, ya buga kwallo ta farko a rami na 16 (da pa 3) a cikin ruwa, inda ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Gwanin golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a dukkan zagayen, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu a tarihin gasar da suka kai 5-0-0, tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a yanzu tun 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Speight ya sha kaye da 5 da 4 daga hannun dan wasan Turai da ke kasa a jerin sunayen 'yan wasa  Torbjörn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ya jagoranci gasar cin kofin duniya, ya sha kaye da 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda wannan ne zai iya zama gasar cin kofin Ryder ta karshe.
Sergio Garcia dan kasar Spain, wanda ya buga gasar Ryder Cup sau takwas, ya zama dan Turai da ya fi samun maki a gasar a duk lokacin da ya kara yawan maki 25.5 a wannan shekara.
